{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "be6482d5-5ff6-4912-9016-9c28fd5be665", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/be6482d5-5ff6-4912-9016-9c28fd5be665@1.pkg/1772597529868/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597530326", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/be6482d5-5ff6-4912-9016-9c28fd5be665@1.pkg/1772597529868/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597530326"}, "identifier": "be6482d5-5ff6-4912-9016-9c28fd5be665", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">本题考查对做好职业准备和职业规划、把握人生关键性选择的认识和把握。</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①③④：即将毕业的初中生在面对升学与就业的选择时，应结合自身实际情况，理性规划未来发展方向；无论是选择职业教育还是普通高中，只要通过努力，不同的成长路径都能为社会贡献力量，①③④说法正确；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②：&ldquo;只有进普高，才能实现人生价值&rdquo; 的说法错误，人生价值的实现途径是多样的，职业院校、就业等不同选择，只要付出努力，都能实现人生价值，②说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">故本题选 C。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）初三毕业后，学生小林结合机械维修兴趣选读职业技校，同学小周依成绩规划升入普高。三年后，小林成为企业技术骨干，小周考入理想大学。这启示我们（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①无论升学还是就业，都要结合自身实际</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②只有进普高，才能实现人生价值</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③要理性规划未来，适时调整发展方向</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④不同成长路径，都能为社会贡献力量</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）初三毕业后，学生小林结合机械维修兴趣选读职业技校，同学小周依成绩规划升入普高。三年后，小林成为企业技术骨干，小周考入理想大学。这启示我们（    ）①无论升学还是就业，都要结合自身实际②只有进普高，才能实现人生价值③要理性规划未来，适时调整发展方向④不同成长路径，都能为社会贡献力量", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/be6482d5-5ff6-4912-9016-9c28fd5be665@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984729333", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②③ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②④ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, 